## ğŸ› ï¸ æŠ€è¡“æ¶æ§‹ (Tech Stack)

æœ¬å°ˆæ¡ˆæ¡ç”¨ç¾ä»£åŒ–å‰å¾Œç«¯åˆ†é›¢æ¶æ§‹ï¼š

* **Frontend**: [Lovable.dev](https://lovable.dev) / React / Tailwind CSS / Shadcn UI
* **Backend / Database**: Supabase (PostgreSQL, Auth, Realtime)
* **AI Engine (RAG)**: AnythingLLM (Vector DB & LLM Orchestration)
* **Workflow**: N8N (Optional, for complex Webhooks)
* **Messaging Platform**: Line Messaging API

